

 ansible is open source resource automation software .Some task that system admin do manually can be possible with using 
 ansible easily . configuration of server , installing software .
 
 ansible configuration is done using different langugaes like python ruby scripting . in ansible there are module available which 
 helps to do configuration like taking backup and copying files. If there is no module present you can create by your own 
 
 to use all thing you need to install ansible software on your machine and python.  Now your machine will become ansible server/  controller
 
